messages.message:
Hi team - at BoFA, we are getting this error message: `Missing optional dependency 'fsspec'` when the customer tries to export to csv. Doing a quick Slack search, I found several old threads that relate to this issue but no conclusive resolution.
• https://instabase.slack.com/archives/CKBRX13L5/p1639653210205400?thread_ts=1639595837.204500&cid=CKBRX13L5
• https://instabase.slack.com/archives/C065BLAST4G/p1701188546040449?thread_ts=1701074665.116599&cid=C065BLAST4G
Was this issue addressed? Is there a workaround?

• what is the customer trying to export as a csv?
• is this in an app? or is this being attempted via an api?
@Serena they are trying to export the ibdoc into a CSV format. The `export_to_csv` is a function in ibtools that faciliates this.

what is the platform version of this BofA environment?

cc @Anil since he responded to the more recent thread
